sources.title: A Christmas Proposal | Full Movie | Christmas 2023 Exclusive | Nicole Eggert
sources.description:
A Christmas Proposal - Two lawyers dueling over a proposal to turn a quaint mountain town into a ski resort discover they are former childhood sweethearts. Lisa is fighting to protect the hamlet; big-city attorney Rick represents the developer who wants to plow it under. But when a car accident forces Rick to stick around, the small town and his former beloved start to work their magic on him.
2008.  Stars: Nicole Eggert, David O'Donnell, Tom Arnold
